data.description: Nice colonial style row house located in Michigan Park ready for your personal touch.  Separate living and dining room, half bath, and kitchen on main level.  Walk out to a fenced in backyard.  Upper level has 3 nice sized bedroom with ample closet space and one full bathroom.  Lower level basement is fully finished with a laundry room and sink.  Property has off street parking.
